examples.en: All their supporters came out for the game.
He is a consistent supporter of the museum.
She is an unabashed supporter of the president's policies.
After he saw the latest development he changed his mind and became a supporter.
President Lyndon B. Johnson was a strong supporter of civil rights.
A staunch supporter of grammatical traditionalism, my English teacher didn't care what the experts in linguistics said.
That tiny country's ambassador from the U.S. is usually some nullity who happens to be a friend or supporter of the current president.
